      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is an exceptional find for anyone seeking a dependable, high-performing driver. Meticulously maintained by a single owner, the engine delivers smooth, responsive power and the transmission shifts seamlessly through every gear. The exterior retains a beautiful, deep gloss, though upon close inspection, you may find the occasional minor stone chip or light surface scratch consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the upholstery is free of tears or significant stains, and every feature\u2014from the crisp infotainment display to the ice-cold air conditioning\u2014operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is sound, having recently passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection and receiving a fresh oil change and filter. The tires have excellent tread depth remaining, and the brakes feel firm and confident. Included with the sale are two sets of keys and a complete folder of service records, proving this car has been cared for with an open checkbook. It is a solid, honest vehicle that is ready to provide years of worry-free service to its next owner.",
